      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 to allow the Attorney General to award grants under a homeland security overtime program to reimburse law enforcement agencies for past overtime expenditures and to require the Attorney General to waive the matching funds requirement for such grants.</title>
